data.description: Move-in ready! 5 bed/3 bath two story home in gated community of Triana. Elegant formal dining room located just off the foyer welcomes you into the home. Kitchen offers rich espresso cabinetry, solid counters, SS appliances, breakfast bar, and breakfast room. Spacious, open living room with high ceiling, great natural light, and exterior access. Vinyl plank flooring throughout the first floor. Primary bedroom down features vaulted ceiling, large oversized tile shower, garden tub, and two tier double vanity. Guest suite downstairs with full bath. Generously sized secondary bedrooms + Gameroom upstairs. Relax under shade of the large covered patio overlooking the private backyard and beautiful greenbelt. Short walk to the community pool and park. Minutes to local shopping and dining in Old Town Helotes, or hiking trails at Madla Natural Area.
